Package: warpture
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: mehranredrose <77771629+mehranredrose@users.noreply.github.com>
Depends: libgtk-3-0, libnotify4, libnss3, libxss1, libxtst6, xdg-utils
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/mehranredrose/WARPture
Description: Cloudflare WARP GUI Manager with App Split Tunneling
 WARPture provides a system tray GUI for managing Cloudflare WARP
 with per-application split tunneling support. Route individual apps
 through or around WARP with a single toggle.
